<LEADPARA>  COLOR them green or color them gone. What will be the color of America's
ancient forests?;   Children and adults can learn about the beauty and
importance of our ancient forests in a coloring book published by the
Wilderness Society (48 pages, $4.95), which also sells ancient forest
T-shirts, tote bags and a colorful illustrated book, "Saving the Ancient
Forests" ($5.95), which tells how we can help preserve these endangered
national treasures.  </LEADPARA>
