a variety of habitats <DATE>Wednesday</DATE> <TIME>mornings</TIME>, <DATE>Sept. 12</DATE> through <DATE>Nov. 14</DATE>, sponsored 
by the <ORGANIZATION>Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History</ORGANIZATION>. Deadline to register is <DATE>Friday</DATE>. 
Call (805) 682-4711. <PERSON>Nona Yates</PERSON> 
</P></TEXT>
